Package ru.nsu.kiryushin

Interface Graph<V>

Type Parameters:
V - vertex value type
All Known Implementing Classes:
AdjListGraph, AdjMatrGraph, IndMatrGraph
public interface Graph<V>
Basic graph contract that supports vertex/edge mutations and iteration. Implementations can be directed or undirected and may support multiedges.
